## 📌 Key Insights

- Electronics, fashion, and beauty are top-performing categories
- Discounts significantly influence purchase behavior
- High ratings and frequent purchases increase spending
- Seasonal spikes occur during major sale events (11.11, 12.12)

---

## 📈 Results Summary

- Model Accuracy (R²): **0.9764**
- Significant predictors: Items Purchased, Rating, Purchase Recency
- 3 Customer clusters successfully identified

